    "markdown": "# Task TRN-30: Image & Asset Generation for Landing Page\n\n## Overview\nThis task documents the prompt design, specifications, and target file outputs for all landing page images and illustrations. The goal is to establish a premium, cohesive, and modern look for Bimbel Triton Denpasar using high-quality flat vector and realistic illustrations.\n\n## \ud83d\udcc2 Target Files & Impact Areas\nAll assets must be saved in the `landingpage/public/` directory:\n- `/hero.png` (Hero banner illustration)\n- `/program-sd.png`, `/program-smp.png`, `/program-sma.png` (Jenjang program illustrations)\n- `/method-1.png`, `/method-2.png`, `/method-3.png` (Method description illustrations)\n- `/alumni-1.png`, `/alumni-2.png`, `/alumni-3.png` (Alumni student avatars)\n- `/gallery-1.png` to `/gallery-6.png` (Suasana belajar gallery grid)\n\n## \u2699\ufe0f Detailed Specifications & AI Prompts\n\n### 1. Hero Banner Illustration\n- **File Name:** `hero.png` (3:2 ratio)\n- **Prompt:** \"A cheerful flat vector illustration of diverse Indonesian high school and middle school students studying together around a table. One student is raising their hand confidently, another is writing notes, one is using a laptop. A friendly teacher stands nearby pointing at a whiteboard with math equations. Surrounding the scene are floating icons: graduation caps, stars, trophies, books, and lightbulbs. Color palette: sky blue, white, navy blue, with warm orange accents. Clean modern edtech style, no text in image, solid white background. 3:2 aspect ratio.\"\n\n### 2. Program Section (Square, 1:1 ratio)\n- **SD Program (`program-sd.png`):** \"A young Indonesian elementary student (age 8-10) happily reading a colorful book with ABC and number blocks around them. Flat vector, modern edtech style, solid white background, square format, no text.\"\n- **SMP Program (`program-smp.png`):** \"An Indonesian middle school student (age 13-15) solving math problems on a notebook, looking focused and confident. Flat vector, modern edtech style, solid white background, square format, no text.\"\n- **SMA Program (`program-sma.png`):** \"An Indonesian high school student (age 16-18) in uniform holding books and a university acceptance letter, looking proud and happy. Flat vector, modern edtech style, solid white background, square format, no text.\"\n\n### 3. Alumni Avatars (Square, 1:1 ratio)\n- **Alumni ITB (`alumni-1.png`):** \"A flat vector portrait style illustration of a young Balinese male student in ITB university shirt, smiling confidently, holding a laptop. Soft chest-up perspective, solid white background, modern and friendly, no text, square format.\"\n- **Alumni UI (`alumni-2.png`):** \"A flat vector portrait style illustration of a young Balinese female student in UI university jacket, holding books and smiling warmly. Soft chest-up perspective, solid white background, modern and friendly, no text, square format.\"\n- **Alumni UGM (`alumni-3.png`):** \"A flat vector portrait style illustration of a young Balinese male student in UGM hoodie giving thumbs up. Soft chest-up perspective, solid white background, modern and friendly, no text, square format.\"\n\n### 4. Method Section (4:3 ratio)\n- **Method 1 (`method-1.png`):** \"A patient and enthusiastic Indonesian teacher explaining a concept on a whiteboard to small group of attentive students. Flat vector, modern edtech style, blue and white color palette, no text, solid white background, 4:3 aspect ratio.\"\n- **Method 2 (`method-2.png`):** \"A student and teacher sitting together looking at a personalized learning plan on a tablet. Warm, collaborative mood. Flat vector, modern edtech style, sky blue and cream colors, no text, solid white background, 4:3 aspect ratio.\"\n- **Method 3 (`method-3.png`):** \"A student using a laptop to take an online quiz, with score results appearing on screen with celebratory stars. Modern UI shown on screen. Flat vector, modern edtech style, blue and white tones, no text, solid white background, 4:3 aspect ratio.\"\n\n### 5. Gallery Images (4:3 ratio)\n1. **Kelas Modern (`gallery-1.png`):** \"Realistic illustration of a bright, clean modern classroom with blue and white walls, Indonesian students in small groups studying with a teacher. Natural light, welcoming atmosphere, solid white background, no text, 4:3 ratio.\"\n2. **Meja Belajar Siswa (`gallery-2.png`):** \"Realistic illustration of a close-up of a student's desk: open textbooks, highlighted notes, a pencil case, and a glass of water. Warm academic atmosphere, solid white background, no text, 4:3 ratio.\"\n3. **Guru Mengajar Matematika (`gallery-3.png`):** \"Realistic illustration of a teacher writing math formulas on a whiteboard, Indonesian students watching attentively. Blue accent walls, modern classroom, solid white background, no text, 4:3 ratio.\"\n4. **Perayaan Lulus UTBK (`gallery-4.png`):** \"Realistic illustration of Indonesian students celebrating, throwing graduation caps in the air outside a modern building with 'Triton' signage. Joyful atmosphere, solid white background, no text, 4:3 ratio.\"\n5. **Area Belajar Kolaboratif (`gallery-5.png`):** \"Realistic illustration of two students studying together with laptops open, smiling, casual seating area with plants and blue decor. Warm atmosphere, solid white background, no text, 4:3 ratio.\"\n6. **Konsultasi Akademik (`gallery-6.png`):** \"Realistic illustration of a friendly consultation between a parent, student, and Triton advisor at a clean modern desk. Professional and warm atmosphere, solid white background, no text, 4:3 ratio.\"\n\n## \u26a1 Verification Plan\n1. **Resolution & Dimensions:** Ensure all generated PNG assets conform to their specified aspect ratios (3:2, 1:1, or 4:3).\n2. **Cohesive Design Style:** Verify that the vector flat illustrations and semi-realistic imagery maintain visual consistency in colors and tone across the landing page.\n3. **Visual Placement:** Ensure all images are loaded correctly inside components without scaling/distortion.\n",
